.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-publish 1  "publish 0.2.0" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-publish \- Publish a built and signed pack to the registry
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp publish\fR [\fB\-\-build\-dir\fR] [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-private\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-token\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] [\fIPATH\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Publish a built and signed pack to the registry
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-build\-dir\fR \fI<DIR>\fR
Directory containing the archive (.tar.gz or .zip), checksums.json, and bundle.sig (default: <pack>/build/)
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-private\fR
Set pack visibility to private
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-token\fR \fI<KEY>\fR
Registry API token
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
[\fIPATH\fR]
Path to the pack directory (defaults to current directory)
.SH VERSION
v0.2.0
